.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH play 1  "play " 
.SH NAME
play \- Play a media element
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBplay\fR [\fB\-\-all\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fITARGET\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Start playback of a media element identified by index (from \*(Aqmedia list\*(Aq) or CSS selector (prefixed with \*(Aqcss:\*(Aq). Returns the updated playback state as JSON. Use \-\-all to play all media elements on the page.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-all\fR
Apply to all media elements on the page
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
.TP
[\fITARGET\fR]
Media element index (from \*(Aqmedia list\*(Aq) or CSS selector (prefixed with \*(Aqcss:\*(Aq)
.SH EXTRA
EXAMPLES:
  # Play by index
  agentchrome media play 0

  # Play by CSS selector
  agentchrome media play css:audio.narration

  # Play all media elements
  agentchrome media play \-\-all
.SH CAPABILITIES
.PP
Media element control (list, play, pause, seek)
.TP
.B media list
List all audio and video elements on the page
.TP
.B media play
Play a media element
.TP
.B target
Media element index (from 'media list') or CSS selector (prefixed with 'css:')
.TP
.B --all
Apply to all media elements on the page
.TP
.B media pause
Pause a media element
.TP
.B target
Media element index (from 'media list') or CSS selector (prefixed with 'css:')
.TP
.B --all
Apply to all media elements on the page
.TP
.B media seek
Seek a media element to a specific time
.TP
.B target
Media element index or CSS selector (not required with --all)
.TP
.B time_pos
Time in seconds to seek to (positional for single target, --time for --all)
.TP
.B --all
Apply to all media elements on the page
.TP
.B --time
Time in seconds to seek to (use with --all)
.TP
.B media seek-end
Seek a media element to its end (duration)
.TP
.B target
Media element index (from 'media list') or CSS selector (prefixed with 'css:')
.TP
.B --all
Apply to all media elements on the page
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Examples:
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media list\`
List all audio and video elements on the page
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media play 0\`
Play the first media element
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media pause 0\`
Pause the first media element
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media seek 0 15.5\`
Seek a media element to 15.5 seconds
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media seek-end --all\`
Seek all media elements to end (skip narration gates)
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media --frame 0 list\`
List media elements inside a specific iframe
.TP
.B \`agentchrome media play css:audio.narration\`
Play a media element by CSS selector
